notesStmt.note: Only European Community legislation printed in the paper edition of the Official Journal of the European Union is deemed authentic.

body.p: to the additional Agreement concerning the validity, for the Principality of Liechtenstein, of the Agreement between the European Economic Community and the Swiss Confederation
HAVE AGREED to make the following amendment to their Additional Agreement of 22 July 1972:
The following shall be deleted: - "Utferdiget i Brussel, tjueandre juli nitten hundre og syttito",
This Supplementary Protocol is drawn up in duplicate in the Danish, Dutch, English, French, German and Italian languages, each of these texts being equally authentic.
